Create a text analyzer which will do below:
1. Generates a summary of unique words and their count
2. Geneates every line where there unique word is found (non-case sensitive)
3. Create a file to store these details
e.g.
input data
----------
I am what I am. I need to do what i need to do.
Output 1:
I   4
am  2
what  2
need 2
to 2
do 2

Output2
I ->
I am what I am
I need ot do what i need to do

am ->
I am what I am.

what ->
I am what I am
I eed to do what i need to do

need ->
I need to do what i need to do

to ->
I need to do what i need to do

do ->
I need to do what i need to do
